| Variable | Description | Default |
|----------|-------------|----------|
| `AI_SUMMARY_DEBUG` | Enable debug logging | `false` |
| `AI_SUMMARY_TIMEOUT` | API request timeout (seconds) | `30` |
| `AI_SUMMARY_MAX_RETRIES` | Maximum API retry attempts | `3` |

